  "instructions": [
    "Soak quinoa in water for at least an hour, then drain. Rinse well.",
    "In a large pot, sauté onions and garlic until soft.",
    "Add bell peppers, black beans, cumin seeds, and lemon juice. Stir well.",
    "Pour in the quinoa, broth, salt, and pepper. Bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat, cover, and simmer for about 20 minutes or until water is absorbed and quinoa is fluffy.",
    "Serve hot."
